{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" strategy used with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":" now uses key-value observing instead of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NotificationCenter"},{"type":"text","text":" when possible. Learn how this may affect your code."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.16"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.6","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.5","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.4"]}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"title":"Migrating to 1.16"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"There are no steps needed to migrate to 1.16 of the Composable Architecture, but there has been","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a change to the underlying behavior of ","type":"text"},{"code":".appStorage","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that one should be aware of. When using","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":".appStorage","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with ","type":"text"},{"code":"@Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", if your key does not contain the characters “.” or “@”, then changes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to that key in ","type":"text"},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be observed using key-value observing (KVO).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Otherwise, ","type":"text"},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used to observe changes.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KVO is a far more efficient way of observing changes to "},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and it works cross-process,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as from widgets and app extensions. However, KVO does not work when the keys contain “.”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or “@”, and so in those cases we must use the cruder tool of "},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". That is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as efficient, and it forces us to perform a thread-hop when the notification is posted before"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"we can update the ","type":"text"},{"code":"@Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" value. For this reason it is not possible to animate changes that are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"made directly to ","type":"text"},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["withAnimation {","  \/\/ ⚠️ This will not animate any SwiftUI views using '@Shared(.appStorage(\"co.pointfree.count\"))'","  UserDefaults.standard.set(0, forKey: \"co.pointfree.count\")","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In general, we recommend using other delimeters for your keys, such as “\/”, “:”, “-”, etc.:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["@Shared(.appStorage(\"co:pointfree:count\")) var count = 0"]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/MigratingTo1.13":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.13","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The Composable Architecture now provides first class tools for building features in UIKit,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"including minimal state observation, presentation and stack navigation.","type":"text"}],"title":"Migrating to 1.13"},"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/ForEachStore":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ForEachStore"}],"title":"ForEachStore","deprecated":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/docum